title: Pushed Into Your Purpose | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Pushed Into Your Purpose | Joel Osteen
description:
God wants to use every situation in your life to prepare you for your purpose. If you'll trust Him through the process, He will take you to a new level of your destiny!

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
